Estimate steepness

H was allowed to be estimated and landed right at 0.99, so the resultant outputs are indistinguishable from the original model (with it fixed). Itâs hard to say at this point whether we have or do not have evidence for density dependence, particularly because this species is so lightly exploited. For now I am OK with leaving the steepness as-is.
